{"id":591641,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【麻辣总局】if-china-肥理儿-the-world-肥理儿/","date":"2018-08-03T09:03:13Z","modified":"2018-08-03T09:03:13Z","title":"【麻辣总局】If China 肥理儿 the World 肥理儿","content":"<p>8月2日，继<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/%E6%A0%A1%E5%8F%8B%E5%91%BC%E5%90%81%E6%B8%85%E5%8D%8E%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%98%E8%83%A1%E9%9E%8D%E9%92%A2-%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%AD%A6%E6%9C%AF%E6%B8%85%E7%99%BD%E9%AB%98%E6%A0%A1%E5%BA%94%E5%8F%91%E5%A3%B0/\">《清华校友：呼吁校长解聘胡鞍钢 维护学术声誉中文互联网》</a>事件之后，中文互联网开始流传多段胡鞍钢英文演讲视频，这些视频中胡鞍钢展现的英语发音尤其“魔性”受到诸多网友的调侃：</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">胡鞍钢讲一口蹩脚的英语🤮 <a href=\"https://t.co/oK7HPXipPV\">pic.twitter.com/oK7HPXipPV</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 夏昙畅 (@VOAJiangHe) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAJiangHe/status/1025283743819423745?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">胡鞍钢教授发言：<br />If China success, the world success. <br />If China 肥理儿，the world 肥理儿&#8230;..</p>\n<p>英文还是不错滴！ <a href=\"https://t.co/0ewizeQ48F\">pic.twitter.com/0ewizeQ48F</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 冰肌玉骨（冰玉） (@bingyuicejade) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bingyuicejade/status/1025197110646333442?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">Better version&#8230;..<br />胡鞍钢叫兽的英文发言应该是“ before international crisis,  the U.S GDP is about 4 times more than China&quot;</p>\n<p>英文翻译机的字幕是“ pay for international crisis, YOUR ASS TV is about &#8230;&#8230;&quot;</p>\n<p>叫兽上国际舞台了！哈哈，老美得上听力课！！！ <a href=\"https://t.co/piP0kjsVqg\">pic.twitter.com/piP0kjsVqg</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Forrest Peng (@pengna76) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/pengna76/status/1025192422031208448?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 3, 2018</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>这些视频出自胡鞍钢2012年的一段演讲《China and the world by 2030》，内容涉及他对《 2030中国：迈向共同富裕》这本书的核心思想的阐释。完整内容如下：</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nTZrTddiISY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,13789],"tags":[33272,35555,33265,30139,12529,35531,19379]}